        Builder used by a DataFactory to construct and initialize a CRUDSocialAgentRegistration. If a Jena resource is provided and there is already a CRUDSocialAgentRegistration at the provided url, the graph of the provided resource will be used. The remote graph will not be updated until CRUDResource.update() is called.
